        <Parent_String>temporary buildings [300165202], temporary structures [300007997], single built works by design [300007962], single built works by specific type [300004795], single built works (built environment) [300004790], Single Built Works (hierarchy name) [300004789], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
